  "text": "Lung nodule is currently a most concerning type of lung lesions. We regard what radiologists see in lung nodules for diagnosing diseases as CT imaging signs, which are also often called \"CT features,\" \"CT findings,\" \"CT patterns,\" or \"CT manifestation.\" These CT imaging signs are very crucial in disease diagnosis and research works [CITATION_1] .",
